Hi-Fi News & Record Review - August 2013

English | pages | HQ PDF | 28.47Mb

Hi-Fi News - The worlds longest-established audio magazine, Hi-Fi News & Record Review was first published in June 1956. Its also the UKs best-selling enthusiast title, and has a global reputation for authoritative, decisive product reviews - covering high-quality home cinema equipment as well as the best in two-channel pure audio. Hi Fi News magazine covers high-end stereo equipment features, music reviews and discussion.
